creditline: Gift of funds from Mary and Bob Mersky
dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: I saw this hawk flying over our heads yesterday, when we delivered food to a donation site. So much care, selflessness and love. Staggering amounts of food shared. And expressions of care and empathy filled the air. We know how to protect each other. The community is strong.
title: June 1, 2020: PROTECT EACH OTHER. (G.F.)
